entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully assisted Mara Jade in locating the Rebel Detainment Facility.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find the crash site near Tyrena on Corellia.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go to the crash site near Tyrena
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Search the passengers and crew for anything that might be useful.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the bodies of the shuttle passengers and crew to see if you can find any important intelligence.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: I've analyzed the data you sent. The shuttle's destination was a previously unknown Rebel Hideout on Corellia. Please investigate a Detainment Facility at that location for me, but be careful.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Go to the Rebel Hideout and find the Detainment Facility.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: The Rebels have been busy haven't they? Come back to Theed, I have a very important mission to discuss with you.
